ompletely trash me at Wii Tennis but I won&#8217;t hold that against him!</p>
<p>We&#8217;ve even taken over a house here in Breckenridge, calling it the Irish House. The Irish Tricolour is flying outside an Irish pub downtown. They might lend it to us if we ask nicely ..<br />
<a href="http://raanan.com">Raanan</a> is staying there too so I guess we&#8217;ll make him an honourary Irishman for the week!</p>
<div align="center"><img src="http://en.blog.files.wordpress.com/2008/10/mcm_2583.jpg?w=600" /></div>
<p>As well as the great PollDaddy news, expect a few more enhancements to WordPress.com soon, and if I have anything to do with it, a plugin or two that will make it into the WordPress MU community too!</p>
