toolscollection.com/?p=4306";s:4:"link";s:88:"http://weblogtoolscollection.com/archives/2008/10/06/wordpress-plugin-releases-for-1006/";s:11:"description";s:3185:"<p><a href="http://kahi.cz/wordpress/ravens-antispam-plugin/"><strong>Raven&#8217;s Antispam</strong></a></p>
<p>Raven&#8217;s antispam is a WordPress plugin, powerful and invisible fighter against comment spam.</p>
<p><a href="http://undeuxoutrois.de/cronjob_control.shtml"><strong>Cronjob Control</strong></a></p>
<p>This plugin shows you all active WP cronjobs (scheduled tasks) of your weblog in the &#8220;Site Admin&#8221; area and if you want, you can stop the cronjob(s)</p>
<p><a href="http://undeuxoutrois.de/wp-db-backup-via-ftp.shtml"><strong>FTP Plugin for WP Database Backup Plugin</strong></a></p>
<p>This plugin adds a fourth way to save the database backup files of the <a href="http://www.ilfilosofo.com/blog/wp-db-backup">WP Database Backup</a> plugin. With the standard <a href="http://www.ilfilosofo.com/blog/wp-db-backup">WP Database Backup</a> plugin you can save the database tables of your weblog a file. This backup file can stored on the server of your weblog, send to an email account or saved (manually) to your local hard disk.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.velvetblues.com/web-development-blog/wordpress-plugin-update-urls/"><strong>Update URLs</strong></a></p>
<p>When you move WordPress to a new domain or directory, the permalinks are not updated. This plugin updates all permalinks. In addition, it also gives the user the option to update any links within posts and pages.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.frank-verhoeven.com/wordpress-plugin-fv-community-news/"><strong>FV Community News</strong></a></p>
<p>Allow your visitors to add articles to the sidebar or anywhere else. Complete with moderation panel and a settings page, you can sit back while you have full control about the look and articles that being posted.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.mydigitallife.info/2008/10/06/caption-disabler-wordpress-plugin-to-disable-and-remove-captions-functionality/"><strong>Caption Disabler</strong></a></p>
<p>Caption Disabler is a WordPress plugin that removes and disables captions feature in WordPress so that all caption shortcode is not been parsed or translated, and no  and  HTML entities are automatically added while editing or writing.</p>
<p><a href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/jquery-reply-to-comment/"><strong>jQuery Reply to Comment</strong></a></p>
<p>Add &#8220;reply&#8221; and &#8220;quote&#8221; features on each comment list.</p>
<p><a href="http://urbangiraffe.com/plugins/redirection/"><strong>Redirection</strong></a></p>
<p>Redirection is a WordPress plugin to manage 301 redirections, keep track of 404 errors, and generally tidy up any loose ends your site may have.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.glockeasymail.com/wordpress-email-newsletter-plugin-for-double-opt-in-subscription/"><strong>WP Double Opt-In List Management</strong></a></p>
